;C     /A/  BEFORE THE FIRST USE OF SMGSM
;C     /B/  IF THE CURRENT VALUES OF IYEAR,IDAY,IHOUR,MIN,ISEC ARE DIFFERENT
;C          FROM THOSE IN THE PRECEDING CALL OF SMGSM
;C
;C
;C                AUTHOR: NIKOLAI A. TSYGANENKO
